@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use the Habit Tracker application.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>We may collect personal information you provide to us such as your name and email address (if account registration is enabled), and habit tracking data including the habits you create, streaks, and completion history.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Data</h4>
    <p>Your data is used solely to provide and improve the Habit Tracker app’s features. This includes tracking your progress, personalizing your dashboard, and improving habit analytics through charts and reports.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">3. Data Storage and Security</h4>
    <p>All your data is securely stored in our database and protected using industry-standard encryption methods. We implement strict access controls to ensure that only authorized personnel can access user data.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">4. Sharing of Information</h4>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties. Your data is private and remains only within the scope of this application.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">5. Cookies and Tracking</h4>
    <p>We may use cookies to improve your experience, such as remembering your theme preferences or login session. No third-party trackers are used.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">6. User Rights</h4>
    <p>You have the right to view, update, or delete your personal data at any time. If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact our support team.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and significant updates will be communicated to users.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">8. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, feel free to reach out to us at <strong>support@habittrackerapp.com</strong>.</p>

    <p class="text-muted mt-5">Last updated: June 4, 2025</p>
</div>
